{"tid":634500,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【港中用字】「綠茶婊」廣東話點表達好？","createTime":"2018-04-19T09:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T00:33:55.000Z","uid":163734,"like":11,"dislike":219,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"0e16a34c3b9b1ffe6ff5ed8049378117d59148f7","tid":634500,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"「綠茶婊」<br />\n綠茶婊是中國大陸網絡流行語，泛指外貌清純脫俗，實質生活糜爛，思想拜金，裝出楚楚可憐，但善於心計，靠出賣肉體上位的妙齡女子。該詞源於指2013年春海南三亞舉辦「海天盛筵」展覽會，引來的嫩模參加，陪睡3天得60萬元人民幣的報酬，網友發明「綠茶婊」一詞加以譏諷，紅爆網絡，其使用範圍亦早已超越海天盛筵事件。<br />\n<br />\n「綠茶婊」勁大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有少少礙眼...<br />\n但如果要用廣東話表達到同樣意思（外貌清純脫俗，實質生活糜爛，思想拜金，裝出楚楚可憐，但善於心計，靠出賣肉體上位的妙齡女子），有邊啲用字比較貼近？！！！"},{"pid":"8de798032a73c2fea0063d22bad6056b63e08cbf","tid":634500,"uid":799,"like":949,"dislike":11,"score":938,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"臭系"},{"pid":"4c33c465310eef03eb814df00c0e314eab22ba5d","tid":634500,"uid":706,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"臭西"},{"pid":"980282b5e500e9af2b0ec29d586b5d2424e8113a","tid":634500,"uid":54812,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"賤人"},{"pid":"279fcaf68fdd13c494885eebb4c77e2eee0ed6e3","tid":634500,"uid":14065,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"臭閪"},{"pid":"440baaf88c50311d7524df847a59d33211a67632","tid":634500,"uid":44454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:43:40.000Z","msg":"純情港女"},{"pid":"0847e32d8b7e3e2d2f2f2978918c51f8c072db83","tid":634500,"uid":64578,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"港女"},{"pid":"5519d38480ee4c029dac6f0a45077e9436093292","tid":634500,"uid":163734,"like":38,"dislike":90,"score":-52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「臭西」無咗表面「清純無辜」嘅意思..."},{